Rees J. Evans, Libelant-Appellant, v. THE Steamship GUL DJEMAL, Her Engines, etc.; Hussein Lufti Bey, Claimant-Appellee. (Circuit Circuit of Appeals, Second Circuit. January 15, 1926.) No. 178.

Before HOUGH, MANTON, and HAND, Circuit Judges.

Henry M. Stevenson, of New York City, for appellant. Purrington & McConnell, of New York City, (John W. Griffin and Frank J. McConnell, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee. PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed (11 F. [2d] 153), with costs.
